Wherther you want to throw a kids birthday party with us or need decoration, you can alwasy rely on us. Celebrating birthdays mean you will have to make a lot of arrangments. Do not panic as we are there for your resuce. 

We are the kids birthday organizer based in Manchester and all over the Northwest. We caters to all the needs of a party whether it is:

  • Balloon Decoration
  • Light Decoration
  • Catering and even cake arrangement

Be it kid's birthday or even your grandma's birthday, we are here to make every moment, a cherished one.

Contact us at: http://www.delhicelebration.com/

Habesha a stunning brand new ladies and gent suited for the any environment; office, social, and special occasions.

A stunning brand new Habesha ladies top suited for the any environment; office, social, and special. Made with high quality 100% White linen with hand loomed fabric made from a millennium old tradition. Couture accents on the sleeves made with the finest aesthetic considerations of balance and elegance. Available in White or Black (default White). 

This is a special order item as the fabric comes from Ethiopia & Eritrea and may take slightly longer to arrive.

Category range includes:

  • DOKA GOLDEN HABESHA DRESS

  • KEREMELA MENEN TELF

  • ZAF MENEN TELF

  • ZUFAN ORGANZA TELF

And many more...

Contact us: http://www.ethiopianclothing.net/ , http://ocacia.com/habesha-clothes.html

Hello, and welcome to Perfect Weddings

Our unique service offers everything you require with regards to venue decoration including premium quality chair covers and sashes, table centres, balloon decoration, twinkling fibre optic backdrops, floral design, drapes, bay trees, hand-crafted stationery and almost anything to help dress your venue the way you want it.

With our offices and showroom based in Altrincham, Cheshire we are well placed to serve all venues in and around the North West. We dress rooms and tables for any special occasion, with particular expertise in Weddings and Corporate Events.
